<body>
  <%- include("../templateParts/nav-bar.ejs"); %>
  <%- include("../templateParts/home-header.ejs"); %>
  <main id="main">
    
    <section id="info" class="info-wrapper">
      <div class="section-heading">
        <h2>A Slice of <span class="txt-orange">India</span> in Burlington</h2>
        <p>Our restaurant offers residents of Burlington a fully immersive Indian dining experience.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="info-section menu">
        <div class="info-details">
          <h3>Traditional Taste</h3>
          <p>We have a menu consisting of carefully selected traditional dishes which originate from North and South
            India. We have a wide range of poultry, lamb, fish and vegetarian curries, and do not serve any pork or
            beef.</p>
          <p>The exotic dishes on our menu include a mix of secret family recipes, which have been passed through
            multiple generations, and homeland comforts.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="info-section bar">
        <div class="info-details">
          <h3>Fully Licensed Bar</h3>
          <p>No true Indian restaurant is complete without a fully equipped bar to match. And we are no different.</p>
          <p>Our bar is fully licensed and is happy to provide you with a wide range of beers (on tap and bottled),
            wines, spirits, juices and mixers.</p>
          <p>We also serve traditional Indian drinks such as Lassi (an Indian milkshake) and chai (tea), as well as bar
            snacks.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="hero-image">
      <div class="hero-content">
        <div class="hero-heading">
          <h2>Discover <span class="txt-red">Something</span> Here</h2>
          <p>Some text to go below what you will discover</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="services" class="services-wrapper">
      <div class="section-heading">
        <h2>A Slice of <span class="txt-orange">India</span> in Burlington</h2>
        <p>Our restaurant offers residents of Burlington a fully immersive Indian dining experience.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="services">
        <div class="service" id="buffet">
          <div class="service-image active" data-value="buffet">
            <p class="service-label">Buffet</p>
          </div>
          <div class="service-panel bg-white hide kill flex" data-value="buffet-text">
            <h3 class="india-font txt-3rem">Lunch Buffet</h3>
            <div class="txt-2rem">
              <p>
                We off a traditional Indian lunch buffet which is sure to satisfy your taste buds and appetite.
              </p>
              <p>
                Our daily lunch buffet costs just $12.99 per person and is unlimited. It features a generous selection
                of traditional curries and sides, as well as rice, dips and salad.
              </p>
              <p>
                For more information about our Indian lunch buffet please see our <a class="service-link" href="/offers"
                  title="Prince of India's special offers">special offers</a>.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="service" id="takeOut">
          <div class="service-image active" data-value="takeout">
            <p class="service-label">Takeout</p>
          </div>
          <div class="service-panel bg-white hide kill flex" data-value="takeout-text">
            <h3 class="india-font txt-3rem">Takeout</h3>
            <div class="txt-2rem">
              <p>
                If you would to eat your food in the comfort of your own home, that's no problem! We provide a full
                traditional Indian takeout service covering the local Burlington area.
              </p>
              <p>
                You can choose to have your food delivered by one of our takeout providers -- <a class="service-link"
                  href="" title="Prince of India on " rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Skip The Dishes</a>, <a
                  class="service-link" href="" title="Prince of India on " rel="noopener noreferrer"
                  target="_blank">Door Dash</a> -- or collect it from our restaurant yourself -- we currently offer a <a
                  class="service-link" href="/offers" title="Prince of India discounts">discount on collections</a>.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="service" id="catering">
          <div class="service-image active" data-value="catering">
            <p class="service-label">Catering</p>
          </div>
          <div class="service-panel bg-white hide kill flex" data-value="catering-text">
            <h3 class="india-font txt-3rem">Catering</h3>
            <div class="txt-2rem">
              <p>
                We are able to provide a traditional Indian catering service for any of your special occasions.
              </p>
              <p>
                Our catering service will enable you to serve all your favorite Indian dishes to your guests, with the
                same high standard you would expect in our restaurant.
              </p>
              <p>
                If you would like to bring the traditional flavours of our Indian cuisine to your event please contact
                us using our <a href="/contact" title="Contact Prince of India" class="service-link">contact form</a>.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="service" id="dineIn">
          <div class="service-image active" data-value="alacarte">
            <p class="service-label">Dining</p>
          </div>
          <div class="service-panel bg-white hide kill flex" data-value="alacarte-text">
            <h3 class="india-font txt-3rem">Dining</h3>
            <div class="txt-2rem">
              <p>
                Our traditional Indian restaurant serves a wide variety of freshly prepared and traditional North and
                South Indian dishes.
              </p>
              <p>
                All dishes have been carefully selected using a mix of secret family recipes and national favorites.
              </p>
              <p>
                We provide our guests with a truly traditional experience and cater to all allergies and we do not keep,
                or serve, any pork or beef on our premises.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
